        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>Dr. Gabriel Ersler was a physician and medical volunteer with the XIII International Brigade (Dombrowski Battalion) during the Spanish Civil War. Collection consists predominantly of photographs he took in Spain as an amateur photographer. A copy of Ersler's 1937-39 photographic log in Polish can be found in Ersler's papers, ALBA #198.</p>
